OL,3,CBusinesses speak out about their
OL,4,Ccustomer footfall
OL,6,FBusinesses from across the region have
OL,7,Fbeen speaking out about their customer
OL,8,Ffootfall over the festive period and
OL,9,Fthe last year.
OL,11,FIt's been predicted that more than
OL,12,F#1.3bn has been spent nationwide as
OL,13,Fshoppers rush to the high street to
OL,14,Fbuy their gifts.
OL,16,FIn Carlisle, retailers say they feel
OL,17,Fpositive about the level of business
OL,18,Fthis Christmas.
