OL,3,CBusinesses speak out about their
OL,4,Ccustomer footfall
OL,6,FDavid Gardiner, from Ashbridge &
OL,7,FBrown, says his business has had their
OL,8,F"best Christmas ever".
OL,10,FHe said: "I know people don't believe
OL,11,Fthat with all the concerns about the
OL,12,Fcity centre, but November and December
OL,13,Fhave been excellent for us."
OL,15,FTerry Foster, from Casanova Menswear,
OL,16,Fsaid: "It's been a slow start and a
OL,17,Flittle bit worrying to kick off but
OL,18,Fthe momentum has got going, so far
OL,19,FI've been okay.
