OL,3,CBusinesses speak out about their
OL,4,Ccustomer footfall
OL,6,F"There's no Christmas market which
OL,7,Falways brings people into the city.
OL,8,FYou also need a satnav to get around
OL,9,Fif you're going to go anywhere - so
OL,10,Fthat hasn't helped.
OL,12,F"We were a bit concerned early on. But
OL,13,Fas I say, it's turned a corner a
OL,14,Flittle bit now. It's not been a
OL,15,Fdisaster. I've done 48 years of
OL,16,FChristmases and we've had mixed bags,
OL,17,Fbut I can't say this is going to be a
OL,18,Fbad one."
