OL,3,CBusinesses speak out about their
OL,4,Ccustomer footfall
OL,6,FSteve Matthews, from Bookends, said:
OL,7,F"We were not expecting something
OL,8,Freally good because Carlisle is
OL,9,Fundergoing such changes - but our
OL,10,Fsales have held up nicely. Our Keswick
OL,11,Fshop has been doing brilliantly.
OL,13,F"I think people are gradually
OL,14,Freturning from that change of habit
OL,15,Fthat came about as a result of COVID.
OL,16,FThe significant thing has been all the
OL,17,Fwork going on at Tullie House because
OL,18,Fwe get lots of customers that visit
OL,19,FTullie and then come to see us.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/10
