OL,6,F"But I think for local people, they
OL,7,Fknow the shops, they know their
OL,8,Froutine and they're not over disturbed
OL,9,Fby the roadworks."
OL,11,FAcross the Border in Dumfries,
OL,12,FStarbucks announced they are closing
OL,13,Fdown their town centre store after
OL,14,Fmore than a decade serving customers.
OL,16,FBusiness owners in Dumfries believe
OL,17,Fthere is no promise of footfall
OL,18,Fimproving on their high street.
