OL,3,CBusinesses speak out about their
OL,4,Ccustomer footfall
OL,6,FColin Barbour, Managing Director of
OL,7,FBarbours, says it has been a "tough
OL,8,Fyear".
OL,10,FHe said: "Trade has gotten harder.
OL,11,FFootfall out on the street has lowered
OL,12,Fand the number of people through the
OL,13,Fdoor is a struggle and a worry."
OL,15,FIn the UK Government's October budget
OL,16,Fin 2024, businesses found out they
OL,17,Fwill have to pay more national
OL,18,Finsurance for every employee they hire
OL,19,Ffrom April 2025. The Government said
OL,20,Fit was a necessary step to better fund
OL,21,Fpublic services.
