OL,3,CBusinesses speak out about their
OL,4,Ccustomer footfall
OL,6,FColin worries it could damage his
OL,7,Fbusiness, he said: "That's going to be
OL,8,Fa major impact for us. We have a lot
OL,9,Fof part-time staff which currently
OL,10,Fonly pay very little in National
OL,11,FInsurance, but as of April it will be
OL,12,Fa big cost to us and it will make the
OL,13,Fbusiness more marginal."
OL,15,FRab Smith, owner of Domino's Record,
OL,16,Fhas experienced a good year in
OL,17,FDumfries due to the comeback of vinyl,
OL,18,Fbut he says the town centre does need
OL,19,Fto become a more attractive place to
OL,20,Fvisit.
