OL,3,CBusinesses speak out about their
OL,4,Ccustomer footfall
OL,6,FHe said: "I think it has gone down a
OL,7,Flong way in the last year. Parking,
OL,8,Fseagulls and flooding is an issue
OL,9,Facross this town.
OL,11,F"People are not using the town centre
OL,12,Fin general. We haven't moved with the
OL,13,Ftimes, a lot of it has to do with the
OL,14,Fchoice of online shopping.
OL,16,F"A lot of people are also going to the
OL,17,Fcities, Carlisle, Glasgow and
OL,18,FEdinburgh because there's more choice.
OL,19,FThere's no question about that.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/10
