OL,6,F"It's just not convenient anymore to
OL,7,Fshop in Dumfries," he added.
OL,9,FTwenty million pounds of UK Government
OL,10,Ffunding is expected to be invested
OL,11,Finto the high street over the next 10
OL,12,Fyears.
OL,14,FDumfries and Galloway Council said in
OL,15,Fa statement: "Our council recognises
OL,16,Fthe challenges faced by high streets
OL,17,Fin towns in our region and across the
OL,18,FUK. In Dumfries, we are committed to
OL,19,Fworking with the Dumfries Town board.
